sql:
SELECT title
FROM job_listings
ORDER BY post_time DESC;

external_knowledge:
- A "full-time job" is typically a job that is at least 30-40 hours a week; 
- "Remote work" means the employee can perform their job tasks outside of the company's standard office environment; 
- The query assumes job_type_id = 1 corresponds to full-time jobs based on external knowledge of the job types.
